Input Image (28x28 pixels)
        |
   Conv Layer → detect edges
        |
     ReLU → keep useful features
        |
   Pooling → keep strongest parts
        |
   Conv Layer → detect complex patterns
        |
     Pooling → again reduce size
        |
     Flatten → 1D vector
        |
